.dateContainer_input_group {
    position: relative;
    /* width: 100%; */
}

.dateContainer_input_group > .input_group {
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
}
.dateContainer_input_group > .input_group > .date_input {
    width: 100%;
}

.dateContainer_input_group > .input_group > .date_input + * {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    position: absolute;
    left:auto;
    right:6px;
    top:4px;
}

.sc_icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 6px;
    left: auto;
    right: 0;
}

.dateContainer {
    position: absolute;
    width: var(--date-width);
    height: var(--date-height);
    background-color: var(--date-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: visible;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px #e2e4e6;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    z-index: 999;
}
/* 
    Header
    default: h1, p, next, prev
 */
.dateContainer .header {
    width: inherit;
    height: 70px;
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    position: relative;
}

.dateContainer .header h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--date-light);
    line-height: 3.2rem;
    margin: 0;
}
.dateContainer .header p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--date-light);
    line-height: 0rem;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
}
/* next prev common, hover */
.dateContainer .header .next,
.dateContainer .header .prev {
    position: absolute;
    color: var(--date-light);
    height: 2rem;
    width: 2rem;
    top: calc(50% - 0.5rem);
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px var(--dark);
    
}
.dateContainer .header .next:hover,
.dateContainer .header .prev:hover {
    background-color: var(--date-light);
    color: var(--date-primary);
}
.dateContainer .header .next {
    left: auto;
    right: 0;
    text-align: center;
}
.dateContainer .header .prev {
    left: 0;
    right: auto;
    text-align: center;
}
/* this class is for date -range only, when from date has a value, this class got implemented there */
.dateContainer .header .prev.disabled_action {
    cursor: default;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 3px var(--dark);
    opacity: 0.7;
}
.dateContainer .header .prev.disabled_action:hover {
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    color: var(--date-light);
}
/* week names class */
.dateContainer .weekdays {
    width: 100%;
    height: 25px;
    padding: 0;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e5e6;
}
.dateContainer .weekdays div {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    width: calc(100% / 7);
    display: block;
    float: left;
    text-align: center;
    height: 100%;
    line-height: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--date-primary);
}
.dateContainer .weekdays div:nth-child(odd) {
    background-color: var(--date-primaryTitle);
}

/* calendar days class */
.dateContainer .days {
    width: 100%;
    height: calc(100% - 95px);
    padding: 0;
    align-items: center;
}

.dateContainer .days div {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    width: calc(100% / 7);
    display: block;
    float: left;
    text-align: center;
    height: calc(100% / 6);
    line-height: 2rem;
    color: var(--date-primary);
    cursor: pointer;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
.dateContainer .days div:hover {
    border: 1px solid var(--date-hover);
}
.dateContainer .days div:nth-child(odd) {
    background-color: var(--date-primaryLight);
}
.dateContainer .days div.prev_days,
.dateContainer .days div.next_days {
    color: rgba(123, 124, 125, 0.4);
}
.dateContainer .days div:hover.prev_days,
.dateContainer .days div:hover.next_days {
    border: 0px solid var(--date-hover);
}
.dateContainer .days div.today {
    background-color: var(--date-highlight);
    color: var(--date-light);
}
.dateContainer .days div.selected_day {
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    color: var(--date-light);
}

.dateContainer .days div.selected_day.today {
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    color: var(--date-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--date-highlight);
}

.dateContainer .days div:nth-child(7n + 1),
.dateContainer .days div:nth-child(7n) {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--weekend);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--weekend);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--weekend);
}
.dateContainer .days div:hover:nth-child(7n + 1),
.dateContainer .days div:hover:nth-child(7n) {
    border: 1px solid var(--date-hover);
}
.dateContainer .days div:hover:nth-child(7n + 1).prev_days,
.dateContainer .days div:hover:nth-child(7n).next_days {
    border: 0px solid var(--date-hover);
}

/* range */
/* for date range when from date has a value */
.dateContainer .days div.disabled_days {
    background-color: var(--date-disabled);
    color: var(--date-light);
    cursor: default;
}
/* when today is inside disabled */
.dateContainer .days div.disabled_days.today {
    border: 1px solid var(--date-highlight);
    color: var(--date-highlight);
}
/* range from from_date to to_date */
.dateContainer .days div.range {
    background-color: var(--date-rangebg);
    color: var(--date-rangetext);
}
/* when today is inside range */
.dateContainer .days div.range.today {
    border: 1px solid var(--date-highlight);
    color: var(--date-highlight);
}
.dateContainer .days div.rangeDate {
    background-color: var(--date-rangeDateBg);
    color: var(--date-light);
}
/* when today is from_date or to_date */
.dateContainer .days div.rangeDate.today {
    border: 1px solid var(--date-highlight);
    color: var(--date-highlight);
}

/* reset button */
.dateContainer .reset-button {
    position: absolute;
    top: 67px;
    left: 100%;
    padding: 0 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--date-primary);
    border-top-right-radius: 4px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    color: var(--date-light);
    font-size: 20px;
}
.dateContainer .ok-button {
    position: absolute;
    top: 100px;
    left: 100%;
    padding: 0 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--date-primary);
    border-top-right-radius: 4px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    color: var(--date-light);
    font-size: 20px;
}
.dateContainer .reset-button:hover, .dateContainer .ok-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--date-light);
    color: var(--date-primary);
}
.dateContainer .reset-button:focus, .dateContainer .ok-button:focus {
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: none;
}
.dateContainer .reset-button span.material-icons, .dateContainer .ok-button span.material-icons {
    font-size: inherit;
    top: 3px;
    position: relative;
}

/* board view */
.month_in_view {
    width: calc((100% / 3) - 10px);
    height: calc(((100% - 80px) / 4) - 10px);
    text-align: center;
    float: left;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 3;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin: 5px;
}
.month_in_view:hover {
    background-color: var(--date-primary);
    color: var(--date-light);
}
.month_in_view.selected {
    background-color: var(--date-highlight);
    color: var(--date-light);
}
.animate {
    overflow: hidden;
}

.closeview {
    animation-name: closeanimation;
    animation-timing-function: ease;
    animation-duration: 0.3s;
}
@keyframes closeanimation {
    0% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
        transform: scale(0);
        opacity: 0;
    }
}
.showview {
    animation-name: showanimation;
    animation-timing-function: ease;
    animation-duration: 0.3s;
}
@keyframes showanimation {
    0% {
        opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 1;
    }
}
.hideview {
    animation-name: hideanimation;
    animation-timing-function: ease;
    animation-duration: 0.3s;
}
@keyframes hideanimation {
    0% {
        opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 0;
    }
}
.hideview-scale {
    animation-name: hideviewScale;
    animation-timing-function: ease;
    animation-duration: 0.3s;
    transform-origin:top;
}
@keyframes hideviewScale {
    0% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0);
    }
}
.hideview-opacity {
    animation-name: hideviewOpacity;
    animation-timing-function: ease;
    animation-duration: 1s;
    transform-origin:top;
}
@keyframes hideviewOpacity {
    0% {
        opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 0;
    }
}

.sc-icons  {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
}
.sc-icons img, .sc-icons svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    vertical-align: middle;
}
